 type="bibl" target="#src_Хаджи-Мурат"/><biblScope>81</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>közbaǧi</w> <gloss><q>чародейство</q></gloss></mentioned> (%iköz%i ‘глаз’ и %ibaǧi%i ‘чародейство’). В осетинский вошла закономерная %bбалкарская%b форма <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>közbaw</w></mentioned>.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 113</biblScope></bibl>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>közbaǧi</w> <gloss><q>sorcery</q></gloss></mentioned> (%iköz%i ‘eye’ and %ibaǧi%i ‘sorcery’). Ossetic acquired the regular %bBalkar%b form <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>közbaw</w></mentioned>.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 113</biblScope></bibl>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>